data.description: Discover a rare gem in a great neighborhood of Arlington - just a mile to all Shirlington has to offer! This condo is a sunlit, move-in ready 875-square-foot upper-level unit in "The Arlington."  The condo has an abundance of light, a new roof, a newly refinished balcony with ample space for an outdoor dining setup or a small herb garden, and two bedrooms. The second bedroom has a  Murphy bed that conveys, providing for a functional work space or second bedroom.  Tucked away in a peaceful spot with a private balcony overlooking trees, ample parking, and in-unit laundry, this cozy abode features a wood burning fireplace, attic storage, and ample closet space.  Enjoy fantastic community amenities like tennis, a swimming pool, and easy access to Shirlington, the W&OD Trail, and a large nearby dog park. Commuting is a breeze with a metro and Pentagon bus stop just around the corner, offering quick access to Old Town, Crystal City, D.C., and major routes like 395 and Route 7. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity – act fast!
